  "title": "Production Worker - WCAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Precisely cut extruded carbon rods to designated block lengths</li>\n  <li>Maintain exceptional quality and precision across all finished products</li>\n  <li>Assemble components in alignment with production standards and specifications</li>\n  <li>Carry out additional tasks as assigned by supervisors as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>12-hour shifts work</li>\n  <li>Comfortable performing repetitive tasks</li>\n  <li>Prior experience with cutting operations using an electric saw is an advantage</li>\n  <li>Requires sustained mental and visual focus with a high level of alertness</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Nyon Hock Sen (Aden)</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124070</p>",
